::Feline::
She looked down and blushed again. "Thank you." She tried to 
straighten up, but still acted shy, "How are you feeling, Better I 
hope. I'm just glad that you made it ok."

::KitKat::

She lay there in stasis lock. Not moving, but still hanging on.

>

> 
> He stayed next to KitKat, doing what ever he could, to keep her 
alive.
